title: Hola Amigos
description: Learn Spanish!  A little chihuahua by the name of Paco has plenty of thrilling adventures planned for little ones learning to speak Spanish in this lively release. Children will hardly notice that they're part of an educational lesson as the animated characters continue to keep them involved and stimulated. With this program geared toward youngsters aged 4 to 9, learning all about a new language has never been easier and more fun!
